<figureCitation box="[721,779,971,993]" captionStart="FIGURES 4–5" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1904,1928]" captionTargetBox="[173,1403,210,1853]" captionTargetId="figure-27@4.[151,1435,181,1880]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 4–5. Merulempista pectinata sp. nov. 4, Adult, paratype, female; 5, Male genitalia, phallus, and 8th abdominal segment, holotype, slide no. LHX13258. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6621360" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6621360/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">Fig. 4</figureCitation>
