<figureCitation box="[579,636,1147,1169]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–3" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[190,1394,202,1899]" captionTargetId="figure-27@2.[162,1426,181,1920]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–3. Merulempista similirubriptera sp. nov. 1, Adult, paratype, male; 2, Wings, paratype, slide no. LHX13259; 3, Male genitalia, phallus, and 8th abdominal segment, holotype, slide no. LHX13253. Scale bar: 1.0 mm." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6621358" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6621358/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="294">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
