<bibRefCitation author="Ren, Y. D. &amp; Liu, S. R. &amp; Li, H. H." box="[1046,1214,1264,1286]" pageId="1" pageNumber="294" pagination="65 - 75" refId="ref4961" refString="Ren, Y. D., Liu, S. R. &amp; Li, H. H. (2011) Review of the genus Merulempista Roesler, 1967 (Lepidoptera, Pyralidae) from China, with description of two new species. ZooKeys, 77, 65 - 75. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 77.938" type="journal article" year="2011">Ren and Li, 2011</bibRefCitation>
